These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel       | satire |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: tomato, grapefruit
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Food           | tomato | grapefruit      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
2 different games are played: snooker, whist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Game          | snooker    | whist   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Hobby      | baking       | collecting |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

